comments: Okoro (CLE) steps out of bounds while still in possession of the ball.
Siakam (TOR) briefly grasps Allen's (CLE) arm as he defends over the pick and immediately disengages as Allen turns to roll.
Siakam (TOR) extends his arms into Allen's (CLE) body and affects his shot attempt at the basket.
As Allen (CLE) contests the driving shot attempt, Barnes (TOR) briefly grasps his extended arm and the contact is marginal.
Okoro (CLE) establishes himself in Barnes' (TOR) path and is firming up when marginal contact occurs as they come together during the pick.
Poeltl (TOR) contests the driving shot attempt and marginal body contact occurs with Mitchell (CLE) after the release.
Strus (CLE) is in a legal guarding position during Barnes's (TOR) drive to the basket.  He reaches across Barnes's non-shooting arm during the shot attempt and the contact is marginal.
Quickley (TOR) and Strus (CLE) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Strus (CLE) reaches in when Quickley (TOR) secures the rebound and the contact is marginal.
Poeltl (TOR) establishes himself in Mitchell's (CLE) path and marginal contact occurs to Mitchell's side as he defends over the pick.
Strus (CLE) jumps for the rebound and incidental contact occurs with Barnes (TOR).
Okoro (CLE) commits a take foul on Barnes (TOR).
Allen (CLE) commits a take foul on Barrett (TOR).
Barrett (TOR) commits a take foul on Mitchell (CLE).  The illegal contact occurs before Mitchell's shooting motion.
Mitchell (CLE) steps across the plane of the free throw line before his free throw attempt contacts the rim.
Siakam (TOR) does not leave the designated throw-in area during the inbound pass.
Strus (CLE) commits a take foul on Barnes (TOR).
